1
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,928
You’re here so fast.

2
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:30,256
You called for me, Mom.

3
00:00:30,288 --> 00:00:31,456
What’s going on?

4
00:00:36,890 --> 00:00:37,888
What is this?

5
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:42,632
Read this and make sure you understand it, then hurry to the meeting room.

6
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:44,624
You’ll need to present this to the board shortly.

7
00:00:46,490 --> 00:00:47,152
Huh?

8
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:50,992
Do your best.

9
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,504
I’ll be listening.

10
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:08,616
Regarding our company’s goals for this quarter, the plan is focused on driving growth.

11
00:01:08,656 --> 00:01:12,544
We will also be expanding our exports

12
00:01:12,576 --> 00:01:17,480
and scaling up to reach more new targets.

13
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:20,424
We are looking to gain fresh perspectives by adopting mindsets

14
00:01:20,464 --> 00:01:25,312
and processes from abroad, from other countries and so on.

15
00:01:25,352 --> 00:01:29,024
I’d like to invite everyone to share your ideas

16
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:31,968
or feedback so that we can present them in our next session.

17
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:38,896
You’re so smart.

18
00:01:38,936 --> 00:01:41,392
The apple doesn’t fall far from the tree.

19
00:01:42,336 --> 00:01:44,888
Oh, you flatter her too much.

20
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:50,024
I mean it. She truly is the new hope of PS Group.

21
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,072
Thank you.

22
00:01:58,192 --> 00:02:02,020
Actually, I have to give all the credit to my mother.

23
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,800
Ranya has always been a humble child like this.

24
00:02:23,376 --> 00:02:24,368
P'Chat...

25
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,640
Where are you going?

26
00:02:27,992 --> 00:02:29,616
They are still talking.

27
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:31,160
How rude of you.

28
00:02:36,336 --> 00:02:37,624
Please, do continue.

29
00:02:42,184 --> 00:02:44,520
What is going on?

30
00:02:45,350 --> 00:02:47,544
Was my presentation really that bad?

31
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:54,312
No. In fact, it was too good.

32
00:03:05,488 --> 00:03:07,490
Are you  in on this with your mother right, Ranya?

33
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:12,928
Huh?

34
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:15,392
What are you doing?

35
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:20,792
In the end, you betrayed me and took your mother’s side, didn't you?

36
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:23,720
I...

37
00:03:27,330 --> 00:03:28,952
I really didn't know

38
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:36,008
The work you just presented, that was my work.

39
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,608
I...

40
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,528
I had no idea...

41
00:03:46,656 --> 00:03:48,660
I don't want to hear your excuses.

42
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,896
But Mom was the one who gave it to me to memorize,

43
00:03:53,450 --> 00:03:55,992
I just did what she told me to do

44
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:57,848
Save your excuses.

45
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,480
Get out.

46
00:04:06,070 --> 00:04:06,856
P’Chat...

47
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,608
please, be reasonable.

48
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,168
Get out!

49
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,408
Ranya

50
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:56,560
Mom...

51
00:04:57,690 --> 00:05:00,064
Mom, how could you do this to me?

52
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:04,752
You knew that proposal belonged to P’Pimchat, didn't you?

53
00:05:07,030 --> 00:05:09,104
It doesn't matter whose plan it was.

54
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:11,560
All that matters is that you presented it well.

55
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:17,192
But Mom... you know this is wrong, right?

56
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,568
I have dinner with the board members.

57
00:05:19,592 --> 00:05:21,536
I won’t be back this evening. That’s all.

58
00:05:51,944 --> 00:05:52,592
P’Chat...

59
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,352
please, be reasonable.

60
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,952
Get out!

61
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:00,152
Ranya.

62
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,032
Help!

63
00:07:03,232 --> 00:07:04,560
Help me!

64
00:07:05,776 --> 00:07:07,780
Someone is locked in here!

65
00:07:09,340 --> 00:07:10,504
Is anyone out there?

66
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:14,560
Please help!

67
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:28,856
P’Chat?

68
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,032
Ranya!

69
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,136
I’m so sorry.

70
00:07:35,410 --> 00:07:37,280
I’m so sorry I took so long to get to you.

71
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,960
Are you hurt anywhere?

72
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,400
I’m okay.

73
00:07:46,592 --> 00:07:48,590
I thought you had already gone home

74
00:07:49,690 --> 00:07:52,048
How could I leave, Ranya?

75
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:56,408
If I’m going home, you’re coming with me.

76
00:08:00,330 --> 00:08:02,784
Don't ever disappear like this again.

77
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:04,584
Thank you.

78
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:10,152
Just knowing you came to save me,I’m so glad.

79
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,448
Of course I came for you.

80
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,304
You’re important to me, Ranya.

81
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:24,632
Let’s go home.

82
00:08:57,048 --> 00:08:58,152
Right now...

83
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:02,912
what I need most is a hug from you.

84
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:20,216
Can you come to me?
